I know ur point,I used to know a mage that didnt like dropping rod during Vulak fight but choose to go nuking.Man she even told every other mage what nuke/dot u should use.It was just a few mobs we mages can do very good dmg on them,like Keeper.After the resist patch mages can do some good dmg with our nukes and pets even on uber mobs.But my point is,if u use those mana to drop rod for wizards and clerics,they can deal greater dmg or save tank's ass.<br>
